      "text": [
        "3064 - وَ قَالَ أَبُو اَلْحَسَنِ مُوسَى بْنُ جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِمَا اَلسَّلاَمُ : «لاَ يُضَحَّى بِشَيْءٍ مِنَ اَلدَّوَاجِنِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3064 - Abu al-Hasan Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) said:\n\"No sacrifice is to be made with any of the domesticated birds.\""
        ]
      }
    }
